text: Chishmy () is a rural locality (a village) in Urshakbashkaramalinsky Selsoviet, Miyakinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 25 as of 2010. There is 1 street. == Geography == It is located 40 km from Kirgiz-Miyaki, 9 km from Urshakbashkaramaly. == References == Category:Rural localities in Miyakinsky District
title: Chishmy, Miyakinsky District, Republic of Bashkortostan
